    "description": "与一只名叫“泰迪”的毛绒熊，以及他的魔法仙女伙伴“莱蒂”，一起体会充满危险的冒险旅程。穿过由邪恶的梦境与扭曲的童话故事构成的噩梦国度，拯救泰迪已经长大的主人艾莉西亚。除了她曾经最爱的玩具之外，还有谁会为了女孩的生命而战呢？<br><br>《至暗童话：深入梦魇》为免费的游戏试玩序章，玩家可以在这个熟悉而又扭曲的世界中，体验泰迪与莱蒂前两章的旅程。您已经准备好离开那尘封的旧玩具箱，接受真正的挑战了吗？您是否有能力，在这充满致命陷阱与嗜血怪物的邪恶土地上大战一场？如果您已经准备好了，就准备翻开童话书的这一页，沉浸在《至暗童话》的故事中吧。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747650/extras/f92565668ccff6e6dfd6f09aac72320f.poster.avif?t=1729061027\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747650/extras/f92565668ccff6e6dfd6f09aac72320f.webm?t=1729061027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747650/extras/f92565668ccff6e6dfd6f09aac72320f.mp4?t=1729061027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>绝无幸福快乐</strong><br>与睡前童话故事中熟悉的人物见面，但别指望对方会拥抱你，亲吻你。狼群渴望鲜血，巨大的魔法豆茎上爬满了虫子和食肉植物，至于小红帽嘛……嗯，她可能会把你切成两半。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747650/extras/1f9aa9314c90ee2f4af7bab74a65f891.poster.avif?t=1729061027\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747650/extras/1f9aa9314c90ee2f4af7bab74a65f891.webm?t=1729061027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747650/extras/1f9aa9314c90ee2f4af7bab74a65f891.mp4?t=1729061027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>泰迪熊的利剪</strong><br>不要被外表所迷惑。或许泰迪看起来软绵绵的，但在莱蒂的帮助下，我们的英雄们会成为强大的二人组合。将旧剪刀变成带有魔力的利剑，将针变成强大的箭矢与抓钩，明智地使用你的法力，这样才能游刃有余地对付敌人。记住，在拯救艾莉西亚的旅程中，使用什么手段都不为过。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747650/extras/d72b2533400196a8a986aad01a03f95e.poster.avif?t=1729061027\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747650/extras/d72b2533400196a8a986aad01a03f95e.webm?t=1729061027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747650/extras/d72b2533400196a8a986aad01a03f95e.mp4?t=1729061027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>前方惟有黑暗</strong><br>游戏的每一章都发生在您所熟悉但遭到扭曲的童话世界中，充满了战斗、障碍与秘密。锻炼您的战斗技巧，对付强悍的敌人，为已经被邪恶力量吞噬的梦境大陆带回希望。获得经验，学习新的技能，扩展您的技能树，抵达噩梦深处，获得胜利。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747650/extras/ffa61f8e39e6d7cd7d9737f7ed86941f.poster.avif?t=1729061027\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747650/extras/ffa61f8e39e6d7cd7d9737f7ed86941f.webm?t=1729061027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747650/extras/ffa61f8e39e6d7cd7d9737f7ed86941f.mp4?t=1729061027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《至暗童话》是一款以深邃的神秘传说为背景的游戏。随着您在故事中不断近战，您将揭开这个噩梦世界背后的秘密。这个故事将如何结束？这将由您来决定。<br>  <br> 您在试玩版中保存的所有进度，都将自动继承至《至暗童话》正式版中。",
